00:36:57.986 --> 00:37:00.716 A:middle
which could possibly just
give you what you need,

00:37:01.156 --> 00:37:02.136 A:middle
go with that first.

00:37:02.326 --> 00:37:04.306 A:middle
I think that's a good idea.

00:37:05.226 --> 00:37:11.326 A:middle
And so the next story,
number six,

00:37:12.516 --> 00:37:13.966 A:middle
is "We Only Need One
