00:38:48.376 --> 00:38:49.916 A:middle
Now we could have more keys.

00:38:49.916 --> 00:38:52.386 A:middle
We had the room for them,
and so you can imagine

00:38:52.386 --> 00:38:54.456 A:middle
that we can start
getting some more keys.

00:38:54.456 --> 00:38:56.916 A:middle
In this case I put in
