So I got to demo this for
Steve, which is a gulp.

00:39:42.906 --> 00:39:46.876 A:middle
And so, so bringing
the iPad, you know,

00:39:46.876 --> 00:39:49.226 A:middle
you kind of have the demo
room, and go in there and he's

00:39:49.226 --> 00:39:50.386 A:middle
in there, and it's
