00:42:45.526 --> 00:42:51.716 A:middle
And so 2012 I joined the effort
to develop iOS 7 and, of course,

00:42:51.716 --> 00:42:57.666 A:middle
as you know one of the big goals
for iOS 7 was a whole new look.

00:42:58.326 --> 00:42:59.846 A:middle
And you ask the question, well,

00:42:59.976 --> 00:43:01.836 A:middle
how do you make all
of these choices?


